pesticide.PPE: long-sleeved shirt; long pants; chemical-resistant gloves made of any waterproof material (except pilots, groundboom applicators, airblast applicators and seed-treatment handlers who are bagging treated seed or sewing bags containing treated seed); shoes and socks; mixers/loaders supporting chemigation applications to turf on sod farms must wear a NIOSH-approved respirator with a dust/mist filter with MSHA/NIOSH approval number prefix TC-21C or any R, P or HE filter

Active_Ingredients.name: mancozeb
Active_Ingredients.mode_Of_Action: A coordination product of zinc ion and manganese ethylene bisdithiocarbamate
